site_title: Leap Frog by Jamie and Micah

block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: Learn how to fold this origami frog! It is the Leap Frog designed by Jamie and her cousin Micah. Sadly, the source of this model does not provide their last names. Either way, this is a fun one/ Try it out yourself. Learn it in less than a minute! Enjoy!!! Thanks For Watching! Wilson Lee @Heap Art
